author: mgrigorov
msg: WICKET-3482 .java files do not show up in the "Source code" popup of the examples
Move the management of resource files from maven-war-plugin to //build/resources.
Now they are copied to target/classes folder and thus visible in the application even when run with jetty maven plugin.
